description:
Star Trek Discovery | Season 3, Episodes 2 & 3: “Far From Home” & “People of Earth”

Season 3 of Discovery is getting goooooood, and joining Anita to discuss all the ways we enjoyed episodes 2 & 3 are special guests and Women Who Warp: Jarrah Hodge and Sarah Gulde. Join us we share our thoughts on characters old and new, make some season predictions, and even experience the catharsis of a good cry. If you’re here for The Hair Report make sure to listen until the end of the podcast where Ebony makes a brief appearance to share her…ah…thoughts.

Links Mentioned:
* Star Trek Quarterly: a fanzine by Trekkies, for Trekkies!  https://www.facebook.com/startrekquarterly.
* Women at Warp: www.womenatwarp.com or @womenatwarp on Twitter, Facebook, and Instagram
